  _displayName: Garage / Basement
  _theme: The band forms in a garage and plays its first backyard show.
  _storyBeatOpen: It starts in the garage. Just you, a beat-up amp, and a handful
    of songs you half-know. Time to make some noise.
  _storyBeatCapstone: "The backyard's packed. You plug in, count off, and for three
    minutes the whole neighborhood is yours. Someone's already asking when the next
    one is \u2014 and a guy named Dave offers to haul your gear. You've got your
    first roadie."
